%% Add-to-cart with merchant-specific price + live availability — Daimler
%% Prices resolved via merchant relation; availability read live from TruckLog / MB LogBus DIMS.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Cust as Customer
    participant Yves as Yves Storefront
    participant Cart as Cart / Price (Zed)
    participant MRel as MerchantB2bContracts
    participant Avail as AvailabilityAdapter
    participant TruckLog as TruckLog / MB LogBus DIMS
    participant Redis as Redis

    Cust->>Yves: Add part to cart (active dealer selected)
    Yves->>Cart: add item + recalculate
    Cart->>MRel: resolve merchant-specific price<br/>(dealer list price / customer discount group)
    MRel-->>Cart: net price (calculated dynamically)

    Yves->>Avail: request availability for SKU + market
    alt TruckLog available for market
        Avail->>TruckLog: availability query [SOAP/REST]
    else fallback
        Avail->>TruckLog: MB LogBus DIMS [REST]
    end
    TruckLog-->>Avail: stock / availability
    Avail-->>Yves: availability (display only, not blocking)

    Cart->>Redis: read cached storage data (product/price)
    Yves-->>Cust: cart line with price + availability
    Note over Yves,TruckLog: Availability is live/read-through (external), NOT stored as Spryker stock.
